_sText:
Well first some Informations:
-More than 100Spawnpoints
-Background music (DJ Lee - Fight very hard)
-Skybox

....

Well there are two sides...Each team spawn on one with no equip.
In the middle of the map is a blade, which is rotating faster and faster.
If it hits you, you will be dead.
Outhside is a night-skybox, and three brushes, which are rotating round the map.
The team, who is still alive, when the other team is dead, wins and a new round will be started......
